  "content": "<span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span>The burden of proving\r\nany fact necessary to be proved in order to enable any person to give evidence of any other fact is on the\r\nperson who wishes to give such evidence</br><hr class=\"hr1\"/>\r\n<span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span><i>Illustrations.</i>\r\n</br><hr class=\"hr1\"/>\r\n<span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span>(a) A wishes to prove a dying declaration by B. A must prove B's death.</br><hr class=\"hr1\"/>\r\n<span style=\"margin-left:15px;\"></span>(b) A wishes to prove, by secondary evidence, the contents of a lost document. A must prove that the\r\ndocument has been lost.\r\n</br><hr class=\"hr1\"/>\r\n</br>",
